title: Roland and Rattfink - Pink Panther Classic Cartoon Collection
description:
MGM has put "The Pink Panther Classic Cartoon Collection" out of print, which makes me a little unhappy, so I went to the trouble and expense to put it back in print. The only way to get some of these discs was to re-buy DVDs some people (like me) had bought once or twice already, because only a few were given individual releases - a real dick move.

This is a .rar of the final volume of the collection, which contains all 17 Roland & Rattfink cartoon shorts. It's a full, uncompressed rip of the Region 1 DVD that should work in any region.

If enough people seed this I'll try to get the other volumes up. Nobody seeding but me = no more volumes from me.
